{"tid":1575932,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"Be the America Hong Kong thinks you are","createTime":"2019-09-17T04:30:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T04:42:56.000Z","uid":214261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5cb7ab4b00b9405b8cd62b02161a978204c08b08","tid":1575932,"uid":214261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T04:30:33.000Z","msg":"除咗「China will pay for its crime against Uighur Muslims」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1571160/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1571160/page/1</a><br />\n「Be the America Hong Kong thinks you are」亦都係一張我覺得重要嘅圖同口號<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CHUbAKm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCHUbAKm.jpg&h=45d962ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n手持國旗、唱美國國歌唔係無用㗎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要鼓動到美國人支持<br />\n美國人自然會比壓力政府<br />\n等政府推行更多有助香港嘅政策<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我反而唔太認同陳雲一派推倡嘅「President Trump please liberate Hong Kong 」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為咁講好易引起反 Trump 嘅人同民主黨人反感<br />\n你知美國國內有幾多人反 Trump 㗎啦<br />\n本來人權法就唔係 Trump 一個人嘅功勞 <br />\n而係美國一眾認同民主自由、支持香港嘅人合力推動嘅法案吖嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「Be the America Hong Kong thinks you are！！」</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"99aea81d9b89155f76bd1073e84ac14be49aa149","tid":1575932,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T04:31:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4125433f4687fd9182ca1b28